BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Wee Build Free Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T180000
UID:711ac2d3f1daf76932887967efc650cf@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:STEM\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nDrop-in program. No registration
  required.Let your child’s imagination soar in this hands-on free play p
 rogram! Designed for kids ages 2-7\, this engaging session provides a crea
 tive and interactive environment where children can explore\, build\, and 
 learn through play. No registration is required.Using vibrant magnetic til
 es and a variety of manipulatives such as blocks\, gears\, and more\, chil
 dren will:Develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills.Enhance fin
 e motor abilities and hand-eye coordination.Foster collaboration and socia
