BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:DATE CHANGE!  Dungeons and Dragons Adventure Club for Kids (Ages 9
 -12 only) #2
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T183000
UID:fa1e0646e953dca6c3e942a3cd4236f9@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Gaming\, Children\, Tweens\n\nTo ensure fair access for as man
 y families as possible\, please read the registration guidelines for this 
 program.One Session Per Month: Patrons may register for only one session o
 f this program per month.Duplicate Registrations: Registrations for more t
 han one session in the same month will be cancelled.We appreciate your und
 erstanding as we work to provide equitable access to this popular program.
 Calling all young adventurers ages 9 to 12! Join us for an exciting journe
 y into the world of Dungeons & Dragons\, where your imagination sets the c
 ourse. Together\, we’ll learn how to create unique characters\, navigate
  magical lands\, and solve thrilling quests. No prior experience is needed
 —new and experienced players alike are welcome!In each session\, you'll 
 explore stories full of mystery\, monsters\, and more all while working as
  a team to overcome challenges and puzzles. Whether you're a brave warrior
 \, a clever wizard\, or a sneaky rogue\, there’s always an adventure wai
 ting. Are you ready to roll the dice and discover where the story leads?Sp
 aces are limited\, so sign up today to secure your spot in our grand adven
 ture! All materials will be provided.Registration will open at 9:00AM on W
 ednesday\, March 25th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter residents and
  on Wednesday\, April 1st for residents of other municipalities.LIBRARY PR
 OGRAM POLICIES:Drop Off Program – This program is intended for children 
 over the age of 9 years who can participate independently. Adult(s) must b
 e present to check in child with youth services staff prior to program. Ad
 ults will not be allowed in the event space. Designated Ages – Please ad
 here to the age restrictions designated on your registration. Only childre
 n in that age range will be admitted.Registration Requirements – To help
  us manage our space\, please register every person who will be attending\
 , including siblings.No Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registrat
 ion for more than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from re
 gistering for future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please c
 ancel your registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the progra
 m to allow for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in
  registration status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to t
 he start of the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The 
 program will begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your sp
 ot will be forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. 
 If spots remain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, r
 egistrants will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the s
 tart time.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center A
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/dungeons-and-dragons-adv
 enture-club-kids-ages-9-12-only-2-168860
