 ve "playscape" based upon a program from the Office of Commonwealth Librar
 ies. Come and enjoy the activities that are set up for this program. It is
  designed for the caregiver to play with the child\, with suggestions for 
 how to enrich the literacy experiences. Children and parents will have the
  opportunity to play with toys\, puzzles and more that connect to the them
 e. Narrative skills and comprehension\, imagination\, spatial and problem-
 solving skills\, phonological awareness\, content area vocabulary and back
 ground knowledge are strengthened as parents and children play and learn t
 ogether.Registration is not required but if space is limited\, registered 
