SUMMARY:Understanding Immigration Law: Naturalization
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T123000
UID:f5970ad619373462cb09ff7abe3bd063@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Discussion\, Presentation\, Adults\n\nRegistration is preferre
 d\; walk-ins will be accommodated as space allows. Best for adults and old
 er interested teens.We welcome local immigration attorney Paige Britton\, 
 who will share her professional experience working within the U.S. immigra
 tion system over several sessions\, exploring a different element each mon
 th.Naturalization – How does someone become a citizen?Learn about the pa
 thways and possibilities for noncitizens to become U.S. citizens under Ame
 rican immigration law. Who may naturalize\, and can you pass the civics te
 st??This event is offered solely as information about the American legal s
 ystem and should not be construed as legal advice. If you need legal couns
 el on this or other immigration matters\, please consult a qualified immig
 ration attorney.
LOCATION:Quarryville\, QVL C.X. Carlson Cultural Room
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/understanding-immigratio
 n-law-naturalizationbecoming-citizen-160892
