  here to help!Join us on the 3rd Thursday of every month at 3:00 PM for ou
 r Genealogy Drop-In Program. Our volunteers will be on hand to help you na
 vigate databases\, interpret census records\, and organize your findings.I
 f you have a specific research goal or a particularly tricky question\, we
  encourage you to reach out to us ahead of time. Providing details in adva
 nce allows us to prepare resources specifically for your search. Send us a
 n email at info@mtpl.info When: 3rd Thursdays at 3:00 PMWhere: Morgan Cent
