 :00AM on Wednesday\, April 8th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter resi
 dents and on Friday\, April 10th for residents of other municipalities.Sto
 rytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration fo
 r more than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from register
 ing for future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel 
 your registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to a
 llow for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in regis
 tration status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the sta
 rt of the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The progra
 m will begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot wil
 l be forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spo
 ts remain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registr
 ants will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start t
 ime.Accompanying Adults – This program is for adults and children to enj
 oy together. Please plan to attend and be engaged with your child. Drop of
 fs will not be permitted.Cancellations- Please check your email prior to d
 eparting to verify that the program has not been cancelled.Program Limits 
 - Patrons are limited to one session of multiple session programs per week
 .
