DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T103000
UID:35e4f2ed4166c6055d34ea73c9e73efa@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\, Children\, Adults\n\nBring the whole fa
 mily to the library for a delightful storytime experience! Perfect for chi
 ldren ages 0-12\, this program features engaging stories\, lively songs\, 
 and fun activities designed to spark a love of reading and learning. This 
 is a wonderful opportunity for families to bond\, build literacy skills\, 
 and create lasting memories together!Adults attending with their child(ren
 ) do NOT need to register. Please add any additional registrants to your r
 egistration if more than one child that will be participating in the progr
 am.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, April 15th for Manheim 
 Township and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, April 17th for reside
 nts of other municipalities.Storytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing 
 to cancel their registration for more than 2 library programs in a month w
 ill be restricted from registering for future programs for a period of one
  month’s time. Please cancel your registrations at least 2 hours prior t
 o the start of the program to allow for those on the waiting list to be no
 tified of their change in registration status.Late Arrivals – Please arr
 ive 10 minutes prior to the start of the program to allow for parking and 
 other circumstances. The program will begin promptly at the designated tim
 e. At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those on the wait list wh
 o will be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants may be allowed into
  the program. However\, registrants will not be permitted to enter the pro
 gram 5 minutes past the start time.Accompanying Adults – This program is
  for adults and children to enjoy together. Please plan to attend and be e
 ngaged with your child. Drop offs will not be permitted.Cancellations- Ple
 ase check your email prior to departing to verify that the program has not
  been cancelled.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/family-story-time-148970
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
