 , helping you recognize the subtle artifacts and patterns indicative of AI
 -generated media. Through hands-on analysis of synthetic images\, deepfake
  videos\, and algorithmically produced news\, you will be able to learn te
 chniques necessary to separate machine-made fiction from human reality. Th
 is class is supported by a grant from the OpenAI Foundation. Ages 18+.
