 join us for stories\, crafts\, and activities!This program contains crafts
  that may be difficult for babies/toddlers\, but we encourage you to try i
 t! They may surprise you. We attempt new motor skills often and encourage 
 parents to help or step back as much as they are comfortable.Family Story 
 Time is a multiple registration type. Please register for any day you plan
  to attend. All (and only) children should be registered. This gives me an
  idea of how many chairs/tables\, as well as supplies. Drop-offs will not 
