  it to Story Time\, please inform Esther Martin by emailing her at emartin
 @manheimlibrary.org. You can also call the front desk at (717)665-6700 Ext
 . 4200. Please let us know as soon as you can because we often have a wait
 list\, and we want everyone to get the chance to participate if possible.
