DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260509T120000
UID:107d20c37cb6eca5487abc5286472bda@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Presentation\, Everyone\n\nThe Penn State Extensio
 n Master Gardeners will guide us through the essentials of seed saving.Com
 e to the library to discover all the reasons to save your own seeds\, meth
 ods for collecting and preserving the seeds\, and the best plants to use t
