BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Parachute Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260515T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260515T104500
UID:78dabfdf86644a479da5a132ca189ce6@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nJoin us for a cooperative m
 ovement program where we will use our imaginations while we play with a pa
 rachute! Stories and songs will be incorporated\, while we move about and 
 use our motor skills. A great activity for young children and their adults
  to come together and share an exciting and engaging play experience! (For
  safety reasons\, children must not be younger than 18 months or older tha
 n 3 years old with an adult\, adult involvement is required)Adults attendi
 ng with their child(ren) do NOT need to register. Please add any additiona
 l registrants to your registration if more than one child that will be par
 ticipating in the program.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, 
 May 6th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, M
 ay 8th for residents of other municipalities.Storytime PoliciesNo Show –
  Patrons failing to cancel their registration for more than 2 library prog
 rams in a month will be restricted from registering for future programs fo
 r a period of one month’s time. Please cancel your registrations at leas
 t 2 hours prior to the start of the program to allow for those on the wait
 ing list to be notified of their change in registration status.Late Arriva
 ls – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of the program to allow
  for parking and other circumstances. The program will begin promptly at t
 he designated time. At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those on
  the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants ma
 y be allowed into the program. However\, registrants will not be permitted
  to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.Accompanying Adults 
 – This program is for adults and children to enjoy together. Please plan
  to attend and be engaged with your child. Drop offs will not be permitted
 .Cancellations- Please check your email prior to departing to verify that 
 the program has not been cancelled.Program Limits - Patrons are limited to
  one session of multiple session programs per week.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148193
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
